from a babe like her.

118
00:07:26.362 --> 00:07:28.948 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hey, there's a babe right here.

119
00:07:29.031 --> 00:07:30.116 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Right, Izumi-kun?

120
00:07:30.199 --> 00:07:34.579 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Nah, you've got nothing
on Tamiya-sensei's mature beauty.

121
00:07:34.662 --> 00:07:38.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
But I guess she prefers guys like Izumi.

122
00:07:38.541 --> 00:07:40.168 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
