123
00:07:40.251 --> 00:07:41.627 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What are you talking about?

124
00:07:41.711 --> 00:07:43.087 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
