125
00:07:49.427 --> 00:07:51.137 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What are you talking about?

126
00:07:51.220 --> 00:07:53.097 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
