127
00:07:55.141 --> 00:07:56.350 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Shinichi.

128
00:07:56.934 --> 00:07:59.812 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
