132
00:08:06.527 --> 00:08:07.987 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Come in, please.

133
00:08:12.825 --> 00:08:17.538 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
