I believe you know what I am.

134
00:08:17.622 --> 00:08:18.498 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yeah.

135
00:08:18.581 --> 00:08:19.832 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
"Yeah"?

136
00:08:20.500 --> 00:08:22.877 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
